{
  "texts": [
    "b, UMAP visualization of the inferred trajectory and pseudotime based on 32-dimensional biological state latent representation in myeloid cells.",
    "c, UMAP visualization colored by imputed gene expression of key cell-type markers.",
    "d, Loess smoothed curve showing trends of C23 along with the pseudotime.",
    "e, Box plots showing C23 values of each cell type in b sorted by the medians (n = 19,405).",
    "In the box plots, the center lines indicate the median, boxes indicate the interquartile range, and whiskers indicate 1.5× interquartile range.f, Heat map showing scaled expression of the top 20 positively and negatively correlated genes of C23."
